-- Zodiac Aerospace Says It Rejected All-Share Takeover Approach From Safran
-- Mark Deen
-- 2010-07-11T15:33:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-11/zodiac-aerospace-says-it-rejected-all-share-takeover-approach-from-safran.html

          
          
             Zodiac Aerospace SA said its board
unanimously rejected a proposal from Safran SA about an
“industrial combination.”  
 Safran’s approach didn’t mention a price, Zodiac said in an
e-mailed statement.  
          
          


  


        